The transactions are settled in dollars which get directly deposited to a merchant’s bank account. According to developer and Zap CEO Jack Mallers, anyone can link their bank account directly to Bitcoin, allowing shoppers to easily spend it and enabling merchants to simply accept it without having to interact with it.💥💥🔽👇🔽.
